Strategic Analysis)

Aquí identificas dónde concentrar esfuerzo.

SQL – Horas por prioridad
SELECT
    Prioridad,
    SUM(Horas_Estimadas) AS total_hours

FROM project_tasks_raw

GROUP BY Prioridad
ORDER BY total_hours DESC;
SQL – Horas por módulo
SELECT
    Modulo,
    SUM(Horas_Estimadas) AS module_hours

FROM project_tasks_raw

GROUP BY Modulo
ORDER BY module_hours DESC;
SQL – Prioridad + módulo
SELECT
    Modulo,
    Prioridad,
    SUM(Horas_Estimadas) AS total_hours

FROM project_tasks_raw

GROUP BY Modulo, Prioridad
ORDER BY total_hours DESC;